Software:

1. One copy of silverfast for the workstation to which the scanner is attached.

For each of the interns' computers we need:

2. jhove (open source)
3. exiftool (open source)
4. Oxygen XML Editor (commercial; academic license)
5. Adobe Photoshop CS 3 or 4 (commercial)
6. Saxon B (not A; open source)
7. md5deep (open source)
8. ichat (comes with operating system)
9. colloquy (open source)

There is a PDF document entitled "workspace-setup.pdf" on the server in the scanned images directory under techgroup that provides more details on the open-source packages.